<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Halo, <%= name %></title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
  <div style="width: 90%; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;">Halo, <%= name %>!</div>

    <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 16px;">
      We're excited to have you get started with Citroën!<br>
      Anda telah mengirimkan permintaan untuk test drive mobil Citroën. Kami akan segera menghubungi Anda.
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 16px;">
      Berikut informasi data anda yang telah kami terima:
    </p>

    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px; font-size: 16px;">
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Nama</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">:</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><%= name %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Email</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">:</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><%= email %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Telepon</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">:</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><%= phone %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Permintaan</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">:</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">Test Drive</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Dealer dipilih</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">:</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><%= dealer %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Model</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;">:</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><%= model %></td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <div style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 18px; color: #555;">
      Jika Anda memiliki pertanyaan lebih lanjut, kami siap membantu! Hubungi kami melalui WhatsApp (<a href="https://wa.me/<%= number %>" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;"><%= phone %></a>). Ini adalah balasan otomatis. Jika Anda membutuhkan respon langsung, silakan kirim email ke care@citroen.indomobil.co.id.
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 18px; color: #555;">
      Bien à vous,<br>
      <span><strong>Citroën!</strong></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
